{
  "texts": [
    "Future workThis paper lays the foundation for our vision of an energyaware and sustainable Green Cloud-Edge continuum.",
    "To develop this further, there are a number of key steps that must be taken.",
    "We discuss three areas of focus for our upcoming future work in this area.",
    "(i) Developing an integrated set of models to enable formal reasoning over energy-aware Continuum systems: This phase focuses on the creation of formal models for federated Cloud-Edge systems and workloads that incorporates energy sustainability, pricing, providers, and consumption.",
    "For the development of such models, we need to identify and categorize the different energy, network, hardware, and software components prevalent in Cloud-Edge systems into a series of interacting layers."
  ]
}